==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trans-
<hw>Trans-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>trans</ets> across,
over.]</ety> <def>A prefix, signifying <xex>over</xex>,
<xex>beyond</xex>, <xex>through and through</xex>, <xex>on the other
side</xex>, as in <xex>trans</xex>alpine, beyond the Alps;
<xex>trans</xex>form, to form through and through, that is, anew,
<xex>trans</xex>figure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transact</ent>⟦br⟧
